  <brief_title>Treatment of a Cancerous Disease of the Peritoneum With Complete Cytoreductive Surgery and Intraperitoneal Chemohyperthermia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Treatment of a Cancerous Disease of the Peritoneum With Complete Cytoreductive Surgery With Intraperitoneal Chemohyperthermia Using Oxaliplatin Plus Irinotecan</official_title>
  <sponsors>
